You could do a technician conveyancer higher apprenticeship and move onto a licensed conveyancer degree apprenticeship.
You could start by doing a project manager degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: After completing your apprenticeship, you would get experience of working in digital delivery teams before taking on a role as a product owner.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could train to be a legal executive through a chartered legal executive degree apprenticeship, or train to be a solicitor through a solicitor degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You could specialise in immigration cases after completing your apprenticeship.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can get into this job through an aircraft maintenance certifying engineering higher apprenticeship.
You can do an advanced print technician apprenticeship.
You may be able to do a science industry process engineer degree apprenticeship.
You could do a lead adult care worker advanced apprenticeship to get into this career and then take further training on the job.
You could do an insurance practitioner advanced apprenticeship.
You could complete an intermediate apprenticeship as a healthcare science assistant.
You could get into this work by doing an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in print finishing.
You can do a level 4 assessor higher apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You'll usually need a level 3 assessor qualification to start, along with a qualification in the subject you want to assess. Employers will also be looking for relevant up-to-date experience.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can do a health care support worker intermediate apprenticeship or a senior healthcare support worker advanced apprenticeship.
You can do a midwife degree apprenticeship.

You can get into this job through a project manager higher or degree apprenticeship.

You can also do a digital and technology solutions degree apprenticeship and move into the role after getting project management experience.
You can do an intermediate apprenticeship as a health care support worker, or advanced apprenticeship as a senior healthcare support worker.
You could complete an advanced early years practitioner apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: Once you have experience as a nursery worker you could apply for a job as a deputy manager or manager.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can get into this role through a degree apprenticeship as a healthcare science practitioner.

You could start by doing an advanced apprenticeship in warehousing and storage.

This will usually take 1 year to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.
You can start by doing a transport planning technician advanced apprenticeship, then move on to a transport planner degree apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in agriculture.
You may be able to do a postgraduate ecologist degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You'll need a qualification and experience in an ecological science to apply.

RelevantSubjects.Html:
You could do a higher or degree apprenticeship in:

  • cyber security
  • cyber intrusion
  • network engineering

FurtherInfo.Html: GCHQ also runs a cyber security degree apprenticeship.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can complete a learning and skills teacher higher apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html:
You'll need a qualification in the subject you want to teach. Employers will be looking for relevant up-to-date industry experience.

You'll also need to show ability in English, maths and IT.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You may be able to start by doing a hospitality manager higher apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You could then apply to become a pub landlord once you've built up your experience in the drinks trade.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could do a furniture design technician advanced apprenticeship to get into interior design.

You can complete a metrology technician advanced apprenticeship.

You can then move on to a senior metrology technician higher apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through a healthcare science practitioner degree apprenticeship.
You can do an engineering pipe fitter or pipe welder advanced apprenticship.
You can get into this job through a financial services customer adviser intermediate apprenticeship.

You could get into this career by taking an intermediate apprenticeship in plastering.

You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.
You could complete an advanced apprenticeship in garment making. You could also move on to a bespoke tailor and cutter higher apprenticeship, as your experience grows.

FurtherInfo.Html: You may be able to get into the industry through the Savile Row Bespoke Association (SRBA) apprenticeship programme. This can take between 2 and 6 years to complete. You would apply directly to SRBA member tailoring companies. Competition for places is strong.

RelevantSubjects.Html:
If you're working in the furniture industry, you may be able to start on a furniture product developer advanced apprenticeship.

You could also do a product design and development degree apprenticeship.
You can work towards this role by starting with an advanced apprenticeship as a broadcast production assistant.
You could work towards this role by doing an intermediate apprenticeship for horticulture and landscape operatives.
You could take a higher apprenticeship as a junior animator. This may help you to get a job as an animation assistant.
You can complete an engineering operative intermediate apprenticeship or a metal casting and foundry technician advanced apprenticeship.
You can get into this job through a hospitality supervisor advanced apprenticeship.
You could specialise in working in hospitals and medical centres by doing a healthcare cleaning operative intermediate apprenticeship.

You may be able to get into this job through an equine groom intermediate apprenticeship.

This will usually take 18 months to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.

FurtherInfo.Html:
If you're aged 16 or over and interested in working in the racing industry, the British Racing School at Newmarket and the National Horseracing College at Doncaster offer pre-apprenticeship foundation courses.

Courses last between 4 and 18 weeks, depending on your experience, and can lead to an apprenticeship in racehorse care and a career as a groom.

RelevantSubjects.Html: If you want to specialise in helping the community with health and wellbeing issues, you may be able to do a public health practitioner degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You could work for organisations like charities, the NHS or local authorities, helping people in communities to live long, healthy and happy lives.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could do a travel consultant advanced apprenticeship.
You could learn some of the skills you would need to get into this job through an early years educator advanced apprenticeship.
You can get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship as a hospitality team member, specialising in housekeeping.
You can get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship as a large goods vehicle driver.
You can get into this career through a postgraduate teaching apprenticeship, if you have a degree.
You may be able to get into this job through an advanced apprenticeship as a recruitment consultant.
You can get into this job through a town planning technical support advanced apprenticeship.
You could do an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship for the children and young people's workforce, or in youth work or care work.
You can complete a leisure team member intermediate apprenticeship to get into this role.
You can get into this job through a fashion and textiles product technologist higher apprenticeship, or specialise in technical textiles through a higher apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through a hospitality team member intermediate apprenticeship.
You can do a thermal insulation operative and technician intermediate or advanced apprenticeship.
You can get into this role through a paramedic degree apprenticeship.

You can get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship as a furniture restorer.

This will usually take 2 years to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.
You could do an advanced apprenticeship in fashion and textiles leather production, or a fashion and textiles product technologist higher apprenticeship.

You could get into this career by completing an advanced apprenticeship in security systems.

You could also do a smart home technician advanced apprenticeship, if you install and set up 'smart' security systems in people's homes. For example, intruder alarms, sensors and monitoring equipment controlled through connected devices.
You may be able to get into this job through a travel consultant advanced apprenticeship.
You could do a chartered surveyor degree apprenticeship.
You could start by doing a digital user experience (UX) professional degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: After completing your apprenticeship, you could find work with a digital design agency or user research company.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can complete a degree apprenticeship in management.
You can complete an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in restoring furniture or advanced upholstery.
You could complete a senior insurance professional degree apprenticeship.

You could get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship in gas industry network operations.

This will usually take 1 year to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.

You may get into this career by doing an intermediate apprenticeship in the water industry.

This will usually take 16 months to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.
You could do a team leader advanced apprenticeship or process leader higher apprenticeship.
You may be able to do a creative industries production management degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You'll usually need experience in production management or production accounting to do this.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could do an advanced apprenticeship in digital engineering.
You could complete a professional economist degree apprenticeship.

You could start by doing an advanced apprenticeship in providing financial services insurance or an insurance practitioner advanced apprenticeship.

You could also take an insurance professional higher apprenticeship, depending on your background and qualifications.
You could get into this role through an intermediate underkeeper apprenticeship.

You could get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship in cleaning and support services.

You could do a specialist healthcare cleaning operative intermediate apprenticeship if you want to work in hospitals.

You could start by doing a non-destructive tester intermediate or advanced apprenticeship.

You could also do a composites technician advanced apprenticeship.
You could take a higher apprenticeship as a hospitality manager if you've got experience in catering and have also worked as a supervisor.

You can get into this job by doing a broadcast production assistant advanced apprenticeship. This can be used to get into a lot of different jobs in film and TV, including costume runner and wardrobe assistant.

You could also do a garment maker advanced apprenticeship, if your job involves repairing and making costumes.

You may be able to start an architectural assistant degree apprenticeship with a company.

This will usually take 4 years to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time studying at a university.

You could also do a design and construction management degree apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in design.
You can do a maritime mechanic intermediate apprenticeship. You will cover both electrical and mechanical engineering work.

FurtherInfo.Html: You would take further training to qualify as an officer after completing your apprenticeship.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can do a hire controller intermediate apprenticeship.
You can get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship as a food and drink process operator, or as a lean manufacturing operative.
You can get into this role through a supply chain warehouse operative intermediate apprenticeship.

You may be able to start through a retailer intermediate apprenticeship or retail team leader advanced apprenticeship before moving into merchandising.

If you already have some retail experience, you could apply to do a buying and merchandising assistant higher or degree apprenticeship.
You can start by doing a junior management consultant apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in animal care.
You can start by doing an advanced apprenticeship in sports coaching.
You could train through an advanced apprenticeship as a mortgage adviser.

You can start by doing a business administrator advanced apprenticeship or school business professional higher apprenticeship.

You can also complete a degree apprenticeship for managers and senior school leaders, depending on your experience.

You could start by doing a Police Constable Degree Apprenticeship (PCDA). It's a 3 year work-based programme that leads to a degree in Professional Policing Practice.

You can apply through your chosen force.

FurtherInfo.Html:
If you want to work in non-emergency response situations you could do a serious and complex crime investigator degree apprenticeship.

In this role, as well as police forces you could also be employed by organisations like:

  • The National Crime Agency
  • Her Majesty's Revenue and Customs
  • The Ministry of Defence

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can get into this job through a pharmacy services assistant or retailer intermediate apprenticeship.

You can complete a software developer higher apprenticeship.

You may be able to do a creative digital design professional degree apprenticeship.
You can work towards this role by starting with an advanced apprenticeship as a junior journalist before specialising in film reviewing and criticism.

You may be able to complete an apprenticeship to qualify as an internal auditor, while working with a company. Training includes:

  • a higher apprenticeship as an internal audit practitioner
  • a level 7 apprenticeship as an internal audit professional
You can get into this role through a degree apprenticeship as an operating department practitioner.

You could start off in a junior data analysis role through a data technician advanced apprenticeship.

You could go on to a data analysis higher apprenticeship.
You could start by doing a telecoms field operative intermediate apprenticeship, or a communications technician or cable installer advanced apprenticeship.
You can get into this job through an advanced apprenticeship as a rail engineering technician. You can do apprenticeships with Network Rail or Transport for London.
You could do a financial adviser higher apprenticeship or a financial services professional degree apprenticeship.
You could take a chartered legal executive higher apprenticeship. You would usually do this after you've completed a paralegal apprenticeship.
You could complete an advanced apprenticeship as a custody and detention officer.
You could get into this job through a commercial procurement and supply higher apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an intermediate and advanced apprenticeship in legal services or as a paralegal.
You can do an occupational therapist degree apprenticeship.
You can get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship as a healthcare support worker.

You can apply for the Civil Service Fast Track Apprenticeship. This is a 2-year higher apprenticeship. There are 6 different career routes:

  • policy
  • business
  • commercial
  • digital, data and technology
  • finance
  • project delivery

You'll usually need GCSEs but some routes require A levels or equivalent qualifications.

You may be able to do a health play specialist higher apprenticeship.

You will need some experience of working with children in a childcare or healthcare setting.

FurtherInfo.Html: There may be opportunities with the NHS, as well as independent and private providers of healthcare services. You can find vacancies through NHS Jobs and the National Association of Health Play Specialists.

RelevantSubjects.Html:
You can complete a rail infrastructure operator or rail engineering operative intermediate apprenticeship.

You can also do a rail engineering technician advanced apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in glass industry fenestration installation.
You can take a housing property assistant intermediate apprenticeship and then a housing and property management advanced apprenticeship.
You can do a packhouse line leader advanced apprenticeship, if you're working on a farming food production line, for example picking and packing fruit and vegetables to order.
You can get into this career through a broadcast production assistant advanced apprenticeship.

You can get into this job through a retail manager higher apprenticeship.

This will usually take 18 months to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.
You can get into this job through a business administrator advanced apprenticeship or a school business professional higher apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an advanced apprenticeship as an ambulance support worker.

You may be able to start on a higher apprenticeship for children, young people and families managers, or care leadership and management, then do further on-the-job training.

You could do a leader in adult care higher apprenticeship.
You can do a fishmonger intermediate apprenticeship.
You may be able to start by doing a laboratory scientist higher or degree apprenticeship.
You can start by doing a retailer intermediate apprenticeship.

You could get into this job through a business administrator advanced apprenticeship.

This will usually take 12 months to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.
You may be able to do a degree apprenticeship in nursing if you work in a healthcare setting like a hospital.

FurtherInfo.Html:
The apprenticeship takes around 4 years and is a mix of academic study and on-the-job training.

You must be supported by your employer to take this route.

RelevantSubjects.Html:
You may be able to start in this job through an intermediate apprenticeship as an express delivery operative with a delivery company.

This apprenticeship will take a minimum of 12 months to complete.

You could start by completing a higher apprenticeship for building services engineering technicians or one for building energy management controls engineers.

You could also do a building services design engineer degree apprenticeship.
You can get into this career through a postgraduate teaching apprenticeship, if you have a degree and want to teach in a secondary school.
You could get into this job through an advanced apprenticeship as a laboratory technician.
You may be able to do an advanced apprenticeship as a workplace pension administrator or a financial services administrator.

You might start your career with a retail team leader advanced apprenticeship or retail manager higher apprenticeship before moving into the buying side.

You could also apply to do a buying and merchandising assistant higher or degree apprenticeship.
You may be able to get into this job through a retailer intermediate apprenticeship.
You could do an air traffic controller higher apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html:
You may be able to get into a similar role through an armed forces apprenticeship.

You can find out more about air traffic control in the armed forces at:Royal Navy; Royal Air Force

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could do an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in court and tribunal administration.

You can get into this job through a horticultural and landscape operative intermediate apprenticeship.

You can also do a packhouse line leader advanced apprenticeship, if you're working on a horticultural production line, for example picking and packing plants and flowers to order.
